data.description: Escape the hustle and bustle of the city and embrace the tranquility of this charming 3 bedroom 2 bath home. The open floor plan allows for seamless flow between the living areas, making it ideal for both relaxation and entertaining. Home has fireplace and built ins. Fully fenced back yard with no back yard neighbors. No carpet in home. Roof is only 2 years old. Close to shopping, restaurants, I220. Call today for your showing.
